nt||at|mitche:  Back to this hand.
When declarer takes the losing trump finesse, North has to decide which suit to lead, clubs or spades.
She should lead a spade, and here is how she should know:
A) South "bid" spades with the "Michaels" 2@h bid, and 
B) since South has length in spades, she is going to be short in clubs.
Declarer will be able to park a losing spade on the long club in dummy.
|
